<h4>About</h4>
	<p>This is the second game that I made on the degree course. 
	The brief was to design a viral game. We made it intentionally score based so users would want to share it with their friends and compare scores.
	We also wanted to make it accessible to established IPs.
	I chose to do the art in MS Paint to achieve a pixel style feel to it which is friendly and yet niche at the same time.</p>

